{"tid":489280,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【性侵連環爆】知名藝人遭性侵又一樁","createTime":"2017-12-04T13:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T08:01:12.000Z","uid":78146,"like":558,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"0e9bffcf784690cb8b6ddf957246eb67742913d4","tid":489280,"uid":78146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:52:36.000Z","msg":"香港田徑女傑呂麗瑤日前在臉書剖白遭前教練性侵經歷，盼社會關注性犯罪，也鼓勵受害者勇敢站出來，社會卻有聲音質疑她事隔多年才公開此事。武師出身出身的藝人麥曾志偉及成龍今天傍晚也在臉書自揭曾遭性侵犯，更稱「不止一次」、「有的是我阻止不了」。他們又解釋因事發在中國大陸，香港法庭沒有司法管轄權，故他們沒有採取進一步行動。成龍回應香港媒體追問時表示，他17、18歲時參加一個交流團到中國大陸，其中一個人趁著無人時做了令她很不快的事，給人佔便宜了，所幸傷害性不太強。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/215129_695ef174577963ea81fb12620d3f6263.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F215129_695ef174577963ea81fb12620d3f6263.jpg&h=41a3cff1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/215130_5dc2b5bfb777b94f2ae1cfcae4f5ff6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F215130_5dc2b5bfb777b94f2ae1cfcae4f5ff6b.jpg&h=a7ab2b64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（以上純屬虛構 如有雷同 實屬巧合）"},{"pid":"3f895ab494775cfb2d0d3bd3ed079e286b645971","tid":489280,"uid":100227,"like":214,"dislike":10,"score":204,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不誠實使用電腦"},{"pid":"71463202eebff28e0d65bacd709d2a2c6a3add6d","tid":489280,"uid":137694,"like":9,"dislike":15,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:58:10.000Z","msg":"好玩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3677dbfacead01f20a3f1876cd0b6163ba280039","tid":489280,"uid":126902,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:00:19.000Z","msg":"以為係容祖兒"},{"pid":"0d9b4aa096c4fcec1e50af4a35f41a4e145b7f46","tid":489280,"uid":51978,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:01:45.0